male genitalia. 13 
<taxonomicName id="26C112A6AB12966381250621662B67FB" genus="C." lsidName="C. umbrata" pageId="1" pageNumber="40" rank="species" species="umbrata">C. umbrata</taxonomicName>
13a ON, Carp Ridge, CNC gen. prep. #16762 13b ON, Manitoulin Is., CNC gen. prep. #16763 14 
